resources that can help them regain their confidence and courage to face life's challenges. For us, it is about creating impact and fostering a sense of hope - where each glimmer of a jewel sold transforms into a ray of hope for someone.<br\/><br\/>Giving light to others is what we are all about. With Solarii Jewelry, you are not just investing in radiant jewels, but you are also a beacon, casting rays of hope and resilience to those in need.<br\/><br\/>That's the magic of Solarii – where each purchase you make illuminates the world a little more, one jewel at a time.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"show_social_links":false,"text_columns":1,"align_text":"text-left","bg_color":"","color":"","heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["text_dUz3BV"],"settings":{"borders":false,"gutters":false,"width":"wrapper--full-padded","height":"image-height","mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","reverse_blocks":false,"color_scheme":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_double_tck6Bi":{"type":"section-double","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","align_heading":"text-left","align_text":"text-left","width":"wrapper--full","align_columns":"flex-align-center","layout":"","grid":3,"layout_mobile":"slider","color_scheme":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"section_announcement_pKEW4V":{"type":"section-announcement","blocks":{"text_HhDU4H":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h4><strong>Lighting Up Lives<\/strong>: Our Give-Back Program at Solarii Jewelry<\/h4>","text_font_size":"body-x-large","color":"","target_device_enabled":false,"target_device":"mobile"}}},"block_order":["text_HhDU4H"],"settings":{"slider_speed":7,"text_alignment":"center","marquee_speed":100,"direction":"ticker-rtl","message_spacing":10,"show_border":false,"layout":"marquee","color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":9,"padding_bottom":9}},"section_columns_Vb6UdT":{"type":"section-columns","blocks":{"image_qAer8q":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Exodus-Cry_49c8bf12-f304-4fdf-8d58-7d3044c375e6.webp","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Contribution from Sales: Each time a piece from Solarii Jewelry is purchased, part of the proceeds goes towards our give-back fund. This acts as our building block towards making a significant difference.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":1,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"image_czq3Wc":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Compassion-International_0aa696ca-c299-41c3-913c-ddd57c2d02e1.webp","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Identifying Families: We work with trusted charitable organizations who help us identify families and individuals who are in dire need of assistance. This allows us to ensure that the contributions make their way to the right recipients.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":1,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"image_UxJmAh":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Convoy-of-Hope_d4bf0cee-c4b0-49b1-9756-7ae423cc3b52.webp","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Providing Financial Aid: The funds accumulated are then distributed to these families, providing financial relief that may be used towards meeting their basic needs, education, healthcare or other necessities. This aid serves as a lifeline, enabling them to overcome their hardships.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":1,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"image_yKVr4D":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Lighting_Up_Lives_Our_Give-Back_Program_at_Solarii_Jewelry.webp","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>Building Resilience: Our ultimate goal is to provide the underprivileged with more than just temporary relief. We aim to empower them with the means to improve their lives and to foster resilience. The support we provide is designed to give them the hope and courage to strive for a better, more sustainable future.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":1,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["image_qAer8q","image_czq3Wc","image_UxJmAh","image_yKVr4D"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","align_heading":"text-center","align_text":"text-left","sg_gap_desktop":14,"sg_gap_mobile":10,"sg_sidepad_desktop":18,"sg_sidepad_mobile":10,"width":"wrapper--full-padded","align_columns":"flex-align-top","layout":"grid","grid":4,"layout_mobile":"slider","color_scheme":"","padding_top":38,"padding_bottom":0,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"section_text_with_products_JXVijY":{"type":"section-text-with-products","settings":{"subheading":"","heading":"So, every Solarii Jewelry purchase you make not only adds a sparkle to your life, but also lights a beacon of hope in someone else's world.","image_border_radius":20,"width":"wrapper","text_font_size_px_desktop":26,"text_align_desktop":"text-left","text_font_size_px_mobile":19,"text_align_mobile":"text-left--mobile","color_scheme":"","padding_top":0